text: I started this probably 9 months ago.
title: text001

text: And we've gone through so much since then...
title: text001

text: At first I thought maybe you didn't know how much I loved you so I wanted to let you know.
title: text002

text: I honestly didn't think we had decided to end things... I thought we were on a break for 3 months that we would come back from...
title: text003

text: So I apologize for making things harder for you my sweetest Annette.
title: text003

text: I am so very grateful for every second I had with you.
title: text004

text: Hopefully you will feel what I am trying to express because the last few times I've felt I mucked it up.
title: text005

text: Mostly because I've never felt this raw with anyone before but I knew after a week with you I could be happy with only for the rest of my life.
title: text006

text: I saw every woman I'd ever dated in you... I thought it had to be a twin flame connection.
title: text007
